{"type":"message","id":"7588ef26","parentId":"7cd012a4","timestamp":"2026-03-27T00:05:21.062Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_A5hdLhzT9Lui0DWq8OYNZCMc","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Service: systemd (disabled)\nFile logs: /tmp/openclaw/openclaw-2026-03-27.log\n\nConfig (cli): ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\nConfig (service): ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\n\nGateway: bind=loopback (127.0.0.1), port=18789 (env/config)\nProbe target: ws://127.0.0.1:18789\nDashboard: http://127.0.0.1:18789/\nProbe note: Loopback-only gateway; only local clients can connect.\n\nRuntime: unknown (systemctl not available; systemd user services are required on Linux.)\nRPC probe: ok\n\n\nTroubles: run openclaw status\nTroubleshooting: https://docs.openclaw.ai/troubleshooting\nService config looks out of date or non-standard.\nService config issue: Gateway service PATH is not set; the daemon should use a minimal PATH.\nRecommendation: run \"openclaw doctor\" (or \"openclaw doctor --repair\").\nsystemd user services unavailable.\nsystemd user services are unavailable; install/enable systemd or run the gateway under your supervisor.\nIf you're in a container, run the gateway in the foreground instead of `openclaw gateway`.\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"ember-ridge","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"Service: systemd (disabled)\nFile logs: /tmp/openclaw/openclaw-2026-03-27.log\n\nService config looks out of date or non-standard.\nService config issue: Gateway service PATH is not set; the daemon should use a minimal PATH.\nRecommendation: run \"openclaw doctor\" (or \"openclaw doctor --repair\").\nConfig (cli): ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\nConfig (service): ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\n\nGateway: bind=loopback (127.0.0.1), port=18789 (env/config)\nProbe target: ws://127.0.0.1:18789\nDashboard: http://127.0.0.1:18789/\nProbe note: Loopback-only gateway; only local clients can connect.\n\nRuntime: unknown (systemctl not available; systemd user services are required on Linux.)\nRPC probe: ok\n\nsystemd user services unavailable.\nsystemd user services are unavailable; install/enable systemd or run the gateway under your supervisor.\nIf you're in a container, run the gateway in the foreground instead of `openclaw gateway`.\n\nTroubles: run openclaw status\nTroubleshooting: https://docs.openclaw.ai/troubleshooting\n","name":"openclaw gateway"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774569921057}}
{"type":"message","id":"ad9d4db7","parentId":"7588ef26","timestamp":"2026-03-27T00:05:27.077Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"发现问题了！网关服务有问题：\n1. systemd user services unavailable - 系统没有 systemd 用户服务\n2. 服务配置过时或不标准\n3. 网关可能没有正确运行\n\n根据 HEARTBEAT.md 规则，发现问题时需要立即通知熊哥。这不是夜间静默模式能忽略的问题，因为网关服务不正常会影响整个 OpenClaw 的运行。\n\n熊哥，网关服务有问题！需要修复：\n\n1. **问题**：systemd 用户服务不可用，网关服务配置过时\n2. **建议**：运行 `openclaw doctor --repair` 来修复配置\n3. **备选方案**：如果是在容器中，应该在前台运行网关而不是用 `openclaw gateway`\n\n需要我帮你运行修复命令吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":324,"output":165,"cacheRead":12800,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":13289,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774569921063,"responseId":"8e066e25-18ae-4051-ab51-8969a8c3f1fa"}}
